data.description: Newer home, lots of bedrooms and mountain views. This 5 bedroom+office home has the equivalent of 4 bedrooms upstairs (one doesnt have a closet at the moment but it can easily be added or the room converted back into a loft) and downstairs living for the master bedroom with a separate office which looks out onto the courtyard. The courtyard has covered patios and within the home are higher ceilings, ceiling fans in most rooms, and gourmet kitchen with pantry, granite counters, and stone work.
